title: Why Clive’s court tangents ‘belittle his success’: court
snippet: Billionaire Clive Palmer’s human rights might have been impeded because prosecutors failed to disclose documents against him for years, a magistrate has ruled.

title: Collapsed Aussie fashion giant unable to pay $25m court fine
snippet: Although liquidators have uncovered potential insolvent trading and breaches of director duties, the claims have gone unpursued in the absence of funding.

title: Collapsed Aussie fashion giant unable to pay $25m court fine
